source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
List senders with unsubscribe support

Usage: mxr subscriptions [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --limit <LIMIT>    [default: 200]
      --rank             Rank by newsletter ROI: lowest open-rate first, ties broken by archived-unread descending. Highlights the lists most worth dropping
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
